  "notes": "Extremely tall north-south route (10x54 blocks, 20x108 tiles). Player arrives from Route 27 to the south and travels north to the Victory Road Gate / Pokemon League Reception Gate. The west flank has water (Surf required). A Heal House sits mid-route on the east side (warp at tile 15,57). Day-of-Week Siblings house is in the lower section (warp at tile 5,71). Six trainers cover the full length including Cool Trainers Gaven and Beth who offer phone rematches. A Max Elixir item ball and a Fruit Tree are present. Tall grass features Doduo, Sandslash, Ponyta, Raticate, and Arbok (morning/day) or Noctowl and Quagsire (night). Surf water holds Tentacool and Tentacruel."
}
